  "Increase above the pure solvent freezing point": "",
  "Stay the same as the pure solvent freezing point": "",
  "Double compared to the pure solvent freezing point": "",
  "Decrease (freezing point depression occurs)": "",
  "Adding solute lowers the freezing point of a solution below that of the pure solvent. This is called freezing point depression.": "",
