  "Water left the carrot cells by osmosis toward the higher salt concentration": "",
  "The salt dissolved the cell walls of the carrot chemically": "",
  "The carrot absorbed salt which made it heavier and limp": "",
  "Osmosis caused water to move out of the carrot cells (lower solute concentration) into the salty solution (higher solute concentration) through the cell membranes, causing the carrot to shrivel.": "",
  "A student compares 1 M NaCl, 1 M KBr, and 1 M glucose solutions. Which would have the highest boiling point?": "",
  "1 M glucose because molecular compounds have the highest boiling point": "",
