  "It only raises the boiling point in summer and has no winter benefit": "",
  "It replaces water completely so there is nothing to freeze or boil": "",
  "Antifreeze causes freezing point depression (prevents freezing in winter) and boiling point elevation (prevents boiling over in summer). Both are colligative properties.": "",
